					"body": "{html}<div><p>by searching getDescription, I found several places in java code\nhandles this<br>\none is<br>\nAppInfo.java is auto generated.<br></p>\n<pre>\n<code>   public String getDescription() {\n           return \"${app_info['description']}\";\n   }</code>\n</pre>\n<p>others are all just return save string</p>\n<p>is there a doc about the call path of js calls?<br>\nsuch as how Titanium.App.getDescription() runs in the\nappcelerator?</p></div>{html}",
